On this page you can configure all the fields from Microsoft to be mapped with fields in Open Social.
        When a user logs in we will try to collect data from your Microsoft instance based on the Microsoft user property
        and import that data in to the user's Profile within Open Social based on the mapping field you selected. 
        Note: Some of these fields require a Microsoft Office 365 account for them to work.
